Quote: I hear awful accounts of scab in the Wairau. Only three flocks are said to be clean - Cooper's, Duppa's and Morse's - ... They say it will cost Monro [pounds]800 to clean his own (and I presume yours) and some other flocks which he admits caught it of his.
